  "elementOrder": ["b-label", "b-glass", "b-metal", "b-paper", "b-clay"],
  "definitions": {
    "b-label": {
      "type": "elementHeading",
      "level": 6,
      "text": "MATERIAL VOCABULARY IN DIGITAL UI",
      "align": "left",
      "width": "hug",
      "height": "hug",
      "marginBottom": "0.5rem"
    },
    "b-glass": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Glass\n\nFrosted, translucent, layered. Communicates depth and hierarchy. Popular in macOS and iOS since 2013.\n\n**Affordance signal:** Float, panel, overlay\n\n**Risk:** Over-application flattens depth hierarchy",
      "level": 5,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true,
      "motionTiming": {
        "entrancePreset": "fade",
        "viewport": {
          "amount": 0.2
        },
        "entranceMotion": {
          "transition": {
            "duration": 0.4,
            "delay": 0
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "b-metal": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Metal\n\nReflective, bevelled, rigid. Communicates permanence and system-level authority.\n\n**Affordance signal:** Controls, hardware, high-stakes action\n\n**Risk:** Cold affect; poor in contexts requiring warmth",
      "level": 5,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true,
      "motionTiming": {
        "entrancePreset": "fade",
        "viewport": {
          "amount": 0.2
        },
        "entranceMotion": {
          "transition": {
            "duration": 0.4,
            "delay": 0.07
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "b-paper": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Paper\n\nMatte, light-weight, stackable. Communicates content primacy and human authorship.\n\n**Affordance signal:** Document, card, editable surface\n\n**Risk:** Insufficient contrast in ambient-heavy environments",
      "level": 5,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true,
      "motionTiming": {
        "entrancePreset": "fade",
        "viewport": {
          "amount": 0.2
        },
        "entranceMotion": {
          "transition": {
            "duration": 0.4,
            "delay": 0.14
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "b-clay": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Clay / Neumorphic\n\nSoft extruded form from background. Communicates tangibility and physical press.\n\n**Affordance signal:** Toggle, button, knob\n\n**Risk:** Fails WCAG contrast; dated by 2022",
      "level": 5,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true,
      "motionTiming": {
        "entrancePreset": "fade",
        "viewport": {
          "amount": 0.2
        },
        "entranceMotion": {
          "transition": {
            "duration": 0.4,
            "delay": 0.21
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "gridMode": {
    "mobile": "columns",
    "desktop": "grid"
  },
  "gridDebug": false,
  "columnAssignments": {
    "mobile": {
      "b-label": 0,
      "b-glass": 0,
      "b-metal": 0,
